"Change Set:		9220MonticelloConfigurations-mpe.74MonticelloConfigurations-mpe.74:if the preference #logToFile is disabled all update log events will be forwarded to a Transcript. If no Transcript is already open, I will open a new one. (requires the collection-mpe.290 extension)"!!MCConfiguration methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'mp 2/2/2010 20:38'!log	"Answer the receiver's log. If no log exist use the default log"		^log ifNil: [		(name notNil and: [ self class logToFile ]) ifFalse: [ 			Transcript countOpenTranscripts = 0 ifTrue: [Transcript open].			^Transcript ].		self log: ((FileStream fileNamed: self logFileName) setToEnd; yourself).		log ]! !